There are whales tweaking the prices like you eloquently stated.  It's nearly impossible for retail investors to time their day trades equal or better to these whales. -the whales are manipulating prices for long term wins
-they want you to day trade and lose at least part of your holdings so they can scoop them up and benefit from their future gains instead of you
-crypto markets have shown long that term success is an extremely high probability
-dont miss out by selling yourself short
-HODL and enjoy the ride
-dont get sucked into checking prices every 5 minutes
